    "multicolumn_WP8adQ": {
      "type": "multicolumn",
      "blocks": {
        "column_6K9qRd": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/PC_Image_1_2f845b70-da85-4ed1-b91e-0f28e94e9042.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<em>1. The Right Arch Support & Alignment</em>",
            "heading_size": "text-base-xl",
            "text": "<p>Supporting the arch in the proper place is crucial. Looking at your bare feet, the apex of the arch appears to be in the middle of the foot. An X-ray can confirm the apex is actually further back. The contour, position and height of Aetrex’s unique arch support aligns anatomically in the proper place to help support our bodies from the ground up.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": false,
            "highlighted_text": "text",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_GNYqJi": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/PC_Image_2_724035f7-745b-4aa9-8159-bc99d1baf93f.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<em>2. The Right Premium Materials</em>",
            "heading_size": "text-base-xl",
            "text": "<p>Most orthotics available in the market use plastics and other hard, uncomfortable materials. The Aetrex Orthotics Collection utilizes premium, shock absorbing materials designed to cushion and support the body while protecting the foot. The collection integrates high-tech, light-weight, modern materials such as memory foams, polyurethanes, and slow recovery foams.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "text",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "column_XRCwq8": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "show_border": false,
            "text_alignment": "center",
            "text_alignment_mobile": "center",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/PC_Image_3_b38963e6-808b-4660-9337-c2e56d16c1b6.jpg",
            "image_ratio": "adapt",
            "heading": "<em>3. The Right Experience & Technology</em>",
            "heading_size": "text-base-xl",
            "text": "<p>Aetrex is the global leader in foot scanning technology and orthotics. Backed by 70-years of data and expertise, Aetrex’s has remained dedicated to advancements in foot health and comfort. Every Orthotic is carefully designed to help relieve common foot pain like Plantar fasciitis, Metatarsalgia, Arch & Heel Pain.<br/></p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "button_style": "secondary",
            "button_external": false,
            "button_icon": true,
            "highlighted_text": "text",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
      },
